data.description: Upgraded kitchen with granite counter-tops; upgraded tiled bathroom; crown molding throughout; rear doors to yard 8ft. ; new deck; fence; brand new custom Anderson Windows throughout house; freshly painted
data.whatILove: The amenities are well kept.  There is a beautiful pool that is kept  like a resort.  There is a beautiful private  meadow with private playgrounds for children.   It's a wonderful place to raise a family.  This block in particular is like a lollypop.  There are no other streets intersecting so it doesn't feel as tight as the other houses in this development.
